\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 349}, {\"ngram\": \"the ParisOlympics\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley announced his decision on Monday to British Vogue before giving an emotional interview with the BBC as he returned to London following the end of the Games in France.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.945541043372247e-31, \"text\": \"British Vogue\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\"}, {\"begin\": 484, \"end\": 487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9801893317354917, \"rank\": 0.020204294494887375, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 506, \"end\": 512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999937899702, \"rank\": 4.348665444357988e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 547, \"end\": 553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9754771162637086, \"rank\": 0.021125025703839898, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 387}, {\"ngram\": \"his decision\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 410}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 420}, {\"ngram\": \"an emotional interview\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 474}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 530}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 was Daley's fifth Olympics in total,winning silver alongside Noah Williamsin the men's 10-metre synchronised platform event.\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0803960710671172e-26, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley's fifth Olympics\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"total\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 617}, {\"ngram\": \"Noah Williamsin\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 643}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 10-metre synchronised platform event\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had previously stepped away from diving after the delayed 2021 Games in Tokyo, where hislong wait for Olympic gold was finally endedalongside Matty Lee.\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 768, \"end\": 773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.7457836132723507, \"rank\": 0.3408715055955665, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 838, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matty Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"the delayed 2021 Games\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"hislong\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Daley had been persuaded to return to the sport in the run-up to Paris, where he medalled again in partnership with Williams, with husband Dustin Lance Black and sons Robbie and Phoenix all watching on from the stands.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 924, \"end\": 929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.0084390778420148e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 998, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dustin Lance Black\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\"}, {\"begin\": 1026, \"end\": 1032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"score\": 0.999987688732586, \"rank\": 9.409943891081803e-06, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\"}, {\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.8490222191008192, \"rank\": 0.17719414918618526, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 864}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"the run-up\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"partnership\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"sons\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had initially hinted that hecould yet go on to a sixth Olympicsin 2028 in Los Angeles, where he now lives with his family.\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1156, \"end\": 1167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999990768629, \"rank\": 7.51459835017018e-10, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Daley has now confirmed that he already knew that the Paris Games would be his last.\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It feels very, very surreal,\\\" Daley said.\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt so incredibly nervous going into this, knowing it was my last Olympics.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my last Olympics\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was a lot of pressure and expectations.\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"expectations\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was eager for it to be done.\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But when I walked out, and saw my husband and kids and my friends and family in the audience, I was like, you know what?\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my husband\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"my friends\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1581}, {\"ngram\": \"the audience\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is exactly why I did this.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1657, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was emotional at the end, up there on the platform, knowing it was going to be my last competitive dive.\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"the platform\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"my last competitive dive\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I have to make the decision at some point, and it feels like the right time.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1850, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"some point\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1849}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the right time to call it a day.\\\"\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1889, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley is the most decorated diver in British history, having also won individual Olympic 10m platform bronze medals at both Tokyo 2020 and London 2012, in addition to another synchro bronze with Daniel Goodfellow in Rio de Janeiro in 2016.\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1928, \"end\": 1943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.7351829182875435, \"rank\": 0.3602057054447272, \"text\": \"British history\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_the_United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2030, \"end\": 2041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1101908880870279e-13, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2086, \"end\": 2103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Goodfellow\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daniel Goodfellow\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Goodfellow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Goodfellow\"}, {\"begin\": 2107, \"end\": 2121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.394235553451399e-17, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"the most decorated diver\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"individual Olympic 10m platform bronze medals\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2006}, {\"ngram\": \"both Tokyo\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2054}, {\"ngram\": \"another synchro bronze\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions Discover a hidden island paradise in the Indian Ocean In addition to his Olympic medals, Daley also won four world titles across individual and team events plus five European Championship titles and five Commonwealth Games medals including four golds in Delhi, Glasgow and the Gold Coast.\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\